%3ECarl%20Jung%20defined%20introverts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20people%20who%20generally%20direct%20their%20interest%20inward%2C%20toward%20their%20own%20thoughts%20and%20feelings.%20Extroverts%20direct%20their%20attention%20toward%20other%20people%20and%20the%20outside%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat's%20key%20is%20that%20introverts%20and%20extroverts%20seek%20energy%20in%20different%20ways.%20Introverts%20like%20to%20recharge%20and%20reflect%20in%20solitude%2C%20avoid%20being%20the%20center%20of%20attention%2C%20and%20often%20prefer%20one-on-one%20friendships.%20Extroverts%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20get%20their%20energy%20from%20being%20around%20other%20people.%20They%20thrive%20in%20crowds%2C%20don't%20mind%20being%20the%20center%20of%20attention%2C%20and%20enjoy%20more%20stimulation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20not%20always%20black%20and%20white%20%E2%80%94%20most%20people%20fall%20somewhere%20in%20the%20middle%20and%20are%20classified%20as%20ambiverts.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20they%20have%20both%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-introverts-guide-to-working-at-home-with-an-extrovert-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eintroverted%20and%20extroverted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20tendencies%2C%20and%20they%20change%20depending%20on%20the%20situation.%20But%20I%20definitely%20lean%20towards%20the%20introverted%20personality%20type.%20While%20I%20love%20being%20with%20people%20and%20hanging%20out%20with%20my%20friends%2C%20I%20need%20my%20alone%20time%20to%20recover.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222570%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Melissa%20Noble%20and%20her%20family%20outside%20walking%20on%20a%20path%20in%20the%20woods.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d86c021d8d2deb96b88718%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221927%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMelissa%20Noble%20likes%20walking%