20but%20he%20returned%20to%20working%20as%20a%20lawyer%20because%20his%20daughter%20was%20born%20and%20he%20wanted%20a%20more%20stable%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202021%2C%20Smith%20landed%20a%20job%20at%20the%20Small%20Business%20Administration%20as%20an%20attorney%20overseeing%20COVID-19%20pandemic-era%20loans.%20His%20salary%20rose%20to%20%24110%2C000%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Smith%20and%20his%20wife%20divorced%20during%20this%20period%20and%20said%20he%20was%20going%20through%20a%20low%20period%20in%20his%20life%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20pandemic%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20see%20friends%20and%20loved%20ones%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20say%2C%20'money%20can't%20buy%20you%20happiness%2C'%20it's%20so%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20point%2C%20Smith%20visited%20the%20Dominican%20Republic%20with%20a%20friend.%20He%20said%20leaving%20the%20US%20made%20him%20realize%20he%20could%20start%20a%20new%20life%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20friends%20were%20shocked%20by%20his%20decision%2C%20especially%20at%20his%20age.%20Some%20even%20said%20he%20was%20making%20a%20mistake%2C%20but%20he%20was%20determined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20said%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20of%20moving%20abroad%20was%20saying%20goodbye%20to%20family%2C%20but%20he%20knew%20a%20major%20change%20in%20life%20would%20help%20his%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFear%20is%20a%20dream%20killer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20that%20point%2C%20I%20said%2C%20'This%20is%20what%20I%20want%20to%20do%2C%20and%20let%20the%20chips%20fall%20where%20they%20may.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2288d1db57-b323-4ed6-b93d-94b709e14a9e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20sense%20of%20financial%20security%20and%20personal%20safety%20abroad%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20moved%20to%20Germany%20without%20a%20job%2C%20living%20off%20the%20money%20he%20made%20selling%20his%20DC%20home.%