20by%20committee%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20had%20to%20convince%20people%20to%20let%20me%20attend%20meetings.%20They%20were%20methodical%20about%20decision-making%2C%20which%20meant%20getting%20things%20done%20took%20longer.%20I%20had%20to%20learn%20to%20do%20things%20completely%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feat-the-frog-promotions-meta-google-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGetting%20promoted%20fast%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Sun%20gave%20me%20too%20much%20confidence.%20Being%20at%20VMware%20humiliated%20me%20because%20I%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20grow%20and%20thrive%20in%20a%20different%20organization%2C%20and%20it%20was%20humbling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20great%20to%20be%20uplifted%20early%20in%20my%20career%2C%20but%20this%20felt%20like%20a%20big%20fall.%20I%20didn't%20feel%20secure%20enough%20to%20ask%20questions%20and%20seek%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20four%20years%20at%20VMware%2C%20but%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsome-truth-nice-guys-finishing-last-work-personality-business-promotions-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enever%20promoted%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20probably%20should%20have%20moved%20up%20during%20my%20last%20year%2C%20but%20I%20also%20think%20I%20was%20catching%20up%20to%20the%20experience%20others%20had%20at%20my%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20before%20joining%20VMware%2C%20I%20co-founded%20a%20consultancy%20company%20called%20Raw%20Engineering%20with%20my%20husband.%20I'd%20already%20been%20helping%20him%20with%20the%20business%20in%20my%20spare%20time%20while%20at%20VMware%20and%20wanted%20to%20return%20to%20being%20a%20founder%2C%20so%20I%20left%20VMware%20and%20became%20Raw%20Engineering's%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20now%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-advice-for-introverts-to-succeed-from-ancestry-ceo-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20anot