or%20customers%20and%20the%20bottom%20line%2C%20with%20branch%20advisors%20averaging%2030%20new%20clients%20a%20year%2C%20according%20to%20Lemkau%2C%20CEO%20of%20JPMorgan%20Wealth%20Management.%20That's%20why%20the%20bank%20plans%20to%20open%20500%20new%20branches%20by%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFoot%20traffic%20is%20down%20but%20not%20down%20as%20much%20as%20you'd%20think.%20It's%20just%20what%20they're%20doing%20is%20different.%20They're%20doing%20transactions%20%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Lemkau%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20her%20phone%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20they're%20looking%20for%20advice%20and%20a%20financial%20relationship%20in%20the%20branch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELemkau%2C%20previously%20JPMorgan's%20CMO%2C%20took%20over%20the%20newly%20reorganized%20US%20wealth%20management%20division%20in%20late%202019.%20Despite%20being%20the%20country's%20largest%20bank%2C%20JPMorgan%20lags%20behind%20its%20peers%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20managing%20money%20for%20affluent%20customers%20who%20are%20not%20rich%20enough%20for%20private%20banking.%20Lemkau's%20mandate%20is%20to%20get%20the%20bank's%2082%20million%20customers%20to%20invest%20their%20money%20with%20JPMorgan%20instead%20of%20with%20competitors%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmorgan-stanley-wealth-management-jed-finn-playbook-etrade-ai-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMorgan%20Stanley%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmerrill-coheads-hans-schimpf-share-playbook-winning-clients-advisors-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMerrill%20Wealth%20Management%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20broad%20strokes%20of%20her%20strategy%20have%20remained%20consistent%3A%20improving%20products%20to%20reach%20clients%20with%20different%20levels%20of%20wealth%20and%20hiring%20more%20advisors%20to%20reach%20customers.%20To%20close%20the%20gap%20between%20self-directed%20investing%20and%20in-person%20advice%2C%20she%20launched%20a%20hybrid%20channel%20that%20offers%20low-cost%20financial%20advice%20via%20phone%20and%20video%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202022.%20As%20for%20head%20count%2C%20the%20number%20of%20advisors%20has%20grown%20by%20more%20than%2030%25%20to%205%2C800%2C%20putting%20her%20on%20track%20to%20meet%20her%20goal%20of%206%2C000%20by%202025.%20Lemkau%20has%20already%20hit%20another%20goal%20of%20doubling%20client%20investment%20assets%20to%20%241%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20killed%20it!%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20with%20a%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20branches%20are%20a%20bigger%20part%20of%20the%20division's%20growth%20than%20she%20originally%20imagined.%20She%20had%20planned%20to%20aggressively%20grow%20JPMorgan%20Advisors%2C%20the%20high-net-worth%20client%20unit%2C%20by%20doubling%20its%20head%20count%20to%201%2C000%20advisors.%20She%20has%20since%20abandoned%20a%20head%20count%20target%20for%20the%20boutique%20unit%2C%20saying%20it%20will%20never%20resemble%20Merrill's%20thundering%20herd%20of%2013%2C000-plus%20advisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-republic-bank-taken-jpmorgan-fdic-fails-find-buyer-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eacquisition%20of%20First%20Republic%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20unit%20has%20just%20under%20700%20advisors.%20But%20growing%20beyond%20that%20by%20recruiting%20top-notch%20teams%20one%20by%20one%20is%20slow%20and%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20almost%20like%20a%20mini%20M%26amp%3BA%20deal%20every%20time%20you%20acquire%20a%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBranch%20advisors%20are%20also%20easier%20to%20retain%20than%20the%20elite%20teams%20that%20make%20up%20the%20high-net-worth%20advisory%20channel.%20This%20spring%2C%20there%20was%20an%20exodus%20of%20First%20Republic%20teams%20before%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20deadline%20to%20move%20their%20assets.%20However%2C%20Lemkau%20said%20more%20than%2080%25%20of%20First%20Republic%20advisors%20remain%20at%20JPMorgan%20as%20of%20August%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20bank%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20choosy%2C%26quot%3B%20touting%20the%20recent%20hire%20of%20a%20%2428%20billion%20team%20from%20Merrill%20Wealth%20Management.%20But%20having%20a%20giant%20book%20is%20not%20enough.%20Lemkau%20wants%20employees%20who%20will%20stick%20around%20for%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20mercenaries%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221820e006-d087-4bce-80c3-0d4aa02309ae%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20you%20can't%20beat%20them%2C%20recruit%20them%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20joined%20JPMorgan%20nearly%2026%20years%20ago%2C%20she%20was%20interested%20in%20a%20short%20commute%2C%20not%20banking.%20(%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20walk%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20quipped.)%20But%20finance%20runs%20in%20her%20family.%20Her%20late%20father%2C%20Curt%2C%20spent%2025%20years%20as%20a%20financial%20advisor%20at%20Merrill%20Lynch.%20Her%20two%20brothers%20have%20made%20their%20mark%20on%20Wall%20Street.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgregg-lemkau-michael-dell-msd-partners-goldman-sachs-trott-bdt-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGregg%3C%2Fa%3E%20runs%20a%20hybrid%20investment%20bank%20that%20caters%20to%20billionaires%2C%20and%20Chip%20is%20a%20managing%20director%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%20in%20private%20wealth%20management.%20(Her%20youngest%20sibling%2C%20Holly%2C%20oversees%20events%20for%20consultant%20Teneo).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20views%20her%20move%20from%20marketing%20to%20wealth%20management%20as%20a%20natural%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20marketer%2C%20your%20job%20is%20to%20grow%20the%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20to%20win%20awards.%20It's%20not%20to%20dance%20on%20tables%20with%20Bon%20Jovi%20at%20Cannes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20a%20JPMorgan%20veteran%2C%20she%20looked%20outward%20to%20build%20her%20leadership%20team.%20Several%20of%20her%20top%20hires%20initially%20turned%20down%20her%20offers%2C%20but%20she%20refused%20to%20take%20no%20for%20an%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20best%20person%20is%20outside%20the%20company%2C%20we%20will%20go%20get%20the%20best%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20turned%20to%20Boaz%20Lahovitsky%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Vanguard's%20robo-advisor%2C%20to%20build%20the%20hybrid%20channel%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-wealth-management-personal-advisors-remote-financial-advice-kristin-lemkau-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJPMorgan%20Personal%20Advisors%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20new%20offering%20has%20led%20to%20billions%20in%20new%20assets%2C%20according%20to%20JPMorgan.%20As%20for%20the%20bank's%20self-directed%20trading%20product%2C%20she%20brought%20in%20Paul%20Vienick%2C%20a%20top%20executive%20at%20TD%20Ameritrade%20who%20also%20helped%20build%20online%20brokerage%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbank-of-america-eliminates-most-merrill-edge-trading-commissions-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMerrill%20Edge%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20fix%20its%20shortcomings%20and%20add%20needed%20features%20like%20fractional%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20really%20nascent%2C%20and%20in%20retrospect%2C%20we%20probably%20shouldn't%20have%20launched%20that%20thing%20until%20it%20has%20closed%20more%20of%20the%20competitive%20gaps%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20the%20bank's%20original%20self-directed%20investing%20product%20launched%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20summer%2C%20Lemkau%20hired%20Anne%20Black%2C%20president%20of%20Goldman%20Sachs's%20charitable%20fund%2C%20to%20advise%20on%20philanthropy%20for%20high-net-worth%20clients%20and%20Jane%20Bailey%2C%20chief%20financial%20officer%20of%20UBS's%20wealth%20business%20in%20the%20Americas%2C%20to%20rein%20in%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20strategy%20is%20not%20one%20that%20I%20would%20replicate%20or%20could%20replicate%2C%20but%20they%20were%20really%2C%20really%20disciplined%20on%20their%20P%26amp%3BL%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20UBS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20turned%20to%20Mollie%20Colavita%2C%20head%20of%20Merrill's%20private%20wealth%20services%2C%20to%20oversee%20best%20practices%20for%20the%20branch-based%20advisors.%20Now%2C%20they%20undergo%20a%20two-year%20coaching%20program%20that%20automatically%20dismisses%20advisors%20who%20fail%20three%20sessions%20in%20a%2012-month%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20machine%2C%26quot%3B%20Lemkau%20said%20of%20the%20branch-based%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22302c5854-b106-4e9c-821d-ff841fefa3bc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBack%20to%20the%20branches%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20her%20focus%20on%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20customers%20to%20invest%20online%2C%20her%20strategy%20is%20analog%20at%20its%20core%2C%20with%20full-service%20advisory%20at%20the%20center.%20The%20division%20shut%20down%20its%20unprofitable%20robo-advisor%20in%20May%20with%20all%20accounts%20converted%20to%20self-directed%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELemkau%20views%20self-directed%20trading%20as%20important%20in%20its%20own%20right%20and%20as%20a%20retention%20tool%20for%20advisory%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20people%20have%20a%20full-service%20advisor%20and%20some%20type%20of%20self-directed%20money%20on%20the%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20we%20frankly%20need%20it%20in%20order%20to%20protect%20the%20full-service%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20circles%20back%20to%20the%20branches.%20Wealth%20Plan%2C%20a%20free%20financial%20planning%20tool%20in%20the%20Chase%20app%2C%20connects%20prospective%20customers%20to%20advisors%20online.%20But%20branch%20bankers%20can%20also%20use%20Wealth%20Plan%20to%20get%20the%20ball%20rolling%20with%20prospective%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20better%20conversation%20for%20the%20banker%20of%2C%20'Hey%2C%20tell%20me%20about%20you%20and%20tell%20me%20about%20what%20you're%20interested%20in'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20better%20conversation%20than%2C%20'Hey%2C%20can%20you%20meet%20my%20friend%2C%20the%20advisor%20up%20the%20hall%3F'%20Which%20sounds%20just%20a%20little%20cheesy%20and%20sales-y.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20all%20goes%20according%20to%20plan%2C%20branch%20advisors%20will%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20new%20products%20in%20order%20to%20focus%20on%20richer%20clients%20with%20%241%20million%20to%20%2410%20million%20in%20investible%20assets%2C%20Lemkau%20said.%20The%20advisors%20can%20direct%20less%20affluent%20clients%20with%20simpler%20needs%20to%20hybrid%20advice%20or%20self-directed%20investing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20sees%20AI%20as%20a%20timesaver%20for%20advisors%20but%20not%20a%20substitute.%20Lemkau%20said%20her%20advisors%20can%20expect%20to%20get%20an%20AI%20productivity%20tool%20that%20helps%20them%20with%20their%20%26quot%3Bhomework%2C%26quot%3B%20aka%20preparing%20for%20client%20meetings%2C%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20is%20concerned%20that%20AI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-racism-bias-new-inclusive-solutions-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eracial%20and%20gender%20bias%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20influence%20its%20financial%20suggestions.%20Moreover%2C%20she%20doesn't%20think%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20market%20for%20AI%20financial%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20see%20it%20replacing%20human%20advice.%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20regulators%20do.%20I%20don't%20think%20that's%20what%20people%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20they'll%20always%20want%20to%20talk%20to%20a%20human.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on