ortsbooks%20also%20complicates%20things.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFootball%20season%20is%20here%2C%20which%20means%20the%20return%20of%20a%20well-worn%20tradition%20in%20my%20home%3A%20Going%20to%20my%20trash%20chute%20to%20place%20sports%20bets.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20might%20wonder%20why.%20I%20live%20in%20the%20great%20state%20of%20New%20York%2C%20where%20online%20sports%20gambling%20has%20been%20legal%20since%202022.%20Placing%20a%20same-game%20parlay%20from%20the%20comfort%20of%20my%20couch%20is%20basically%20a%20right%20at%20this%20point.%20And%20these%20days%20they%20are%20practically%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Ebegging%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20you%20to%20do%20it%20with%20the%20amount%20of%20advertisements%20and%20promos%20you%20see.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20when%20I%20want%20to%20place%20a%20bet%20that%20will%20undoubtedly%20lose%2C%20I%20need%20to%20walk%20to%20my%20building's%20smelly%20trash-chute%20room.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESee%2C%20despite%20living%20in%20New%20York%2C%20I%20am%20close%20enough%20to%20Connecticut%20to%20see%20it%20from%20my%20window.%20(Fancy%2C%20I%20know.)%20But%20because%20my%20sportsbook%20can't%20decipher%20which%20state%20I'm%20in%2C%20it's%20resolved%20to%20block%20my%20access%20entirely.%20(Rude!)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20least%2C%20until%20I%20make%20a%20trip%20to%20the%20trash%20room.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20irony%20is%20online%20sports%20gambling%20is%20legal%20in%20Connecticut%2C%20too!%20So%20regardless%20of%20which%20state%20I%20am%20in%2C%20I%20am%20legally%20allowed%20to%20bet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20However%2C%20I%20need%20to%20take%20an%20extra%20step%20%E2%80%94%20technically%2C%2080%20steps%20(I%20counted)%E2%80%94%20to%20make%20all%20the%20bets%20my%20heart%20desires%20(and%20my%20wallet%20will%20come%20to%20regret).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e4a9078-add0-42c9-92f1-208c695b6313%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDifferent%20state%2C%20different%20gambling%20rules%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20trash-chute%20gambling%20pilgrimage%20is%20specific%20to%20me%2C%20but%20it%20represents%20one%20of%20the%20many%20quirks%20of%20the%20legalized%20gambling%20industry.%20Despite%20sports-betting%20revenue%20hitting%20%2410.92%20billion%20last%20year%2C%20the%20market%20is%20still%20a%20bit%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Efunky%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere's%20another%20fun%20one.%20When%20you're%20in%20New%20York%2C%20you're%20not%20allowed%20to%20bet%20on%20in-state%20colleges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENew%20York's%20not%20alone%2C%20as%20many%20states%20try%20to%20avoid%20college%20athletes%20from%20being%20influenced%20by%20gamblers.%20Some%20states%20do%20allow%20bets%20on%20in-state%20schools%2C%20but%20not%20player-specific%20bets%2C%20commonly%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bprop%20bets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20theory%2C%20that%20makes%20sense.%20The%20execution%2C%20not%20so%20much.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20while%20I%20can't%20bet%20on%20Syracuse%20University%2C%20which%20is%20about%20250%20miles%20from%20my%20home%2C%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Ecan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3Ebet%20on%20the%20handful%20of%20schools%20a%20short%20drive%20up%20I-95%20in%20Connecticut.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20states'%20laws%20are%20even%20more%20peculiar.%20In%20Illinois%2C%20for%20example%2C%20you%20are%20prohibited%20from%20betting%20on%20in-state%20colleges%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eunless%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20you%20place%20the%20bet%20in%20person.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d22d276-6cf0-4c5c-a1e9-fade316648a6%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELeagues%20love%20gambling%20until%20they%20don't%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20what%20makes%20this%20new%20era%20of%20sports%20gambling%20particularly%20confusing%20is%20the%20relationship%20between%20sportsbooks%20and%20the%20leagues%20they're%20setting%20lines%20for.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYears%20ago%2C%20Pete%20Rose%20was%20the%20biggest%20cautionary%20tale%20in%20sports.%20The%20MLB's%20all-time%20hits%20leader%20saw%20his%20legacy%20destroyed%20in%201989%20when%20he%20was%20permanently%20banned%20from%20baseball%20over%20allegations%20he%20bet%20on%20games%20he%20played%20and%20managed%20in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20than%2030%20years%20later%2C%20leagues%20and%20gambling%20companies%20are%20thick%20as%20thieves.%20All%20four%20major%20professional%20sports%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20NFL%2C%20NBA%2C%20MLB%2C%20and%20NHL%20%E2%80%94%20have%20partnership%20deals%20with%20at%20least%20one%20sportsbook.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20active%20players%20are%20getting%20in%20on%20the%20action%2C%20something%20that%20was%20unfathomable%20a%20decade%20ago.%20The%20NBA's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdknetwork.draftkings.com%2F2024%2F02%2F02%2Flebron-james-joins-the-draftkings-family-in-legendary-team-up%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELeBron%20James%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20NHL's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.prnewswire.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fbetmgm-signs-edmonton-oilers-captain-connor-mcdavid-as-brand-ambassador-301496050.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EConnor%20McDavid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20two%20of%20the%20top%20players%20in%20their%20respective%20sports%2C%20both%20cut%20deals%20with%20sportsbooks%20in%20recent%20years.%20What%20a%20time%20to%20be%20alive!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20despite%20all%20the%20promotion%20(and%20sponsorship%20money)%20touting%20sports%20gambling%2C%20athletes%20betting%20on%20their%20own%20games%20is%20still%20very%20much%20banned.%20All%20f