n%3E%3Cp%3ESteve%20Eisman%2C%20Neuberger%20Berman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce-in-a-lifetime%20trades%20are%20called%20that%20for%20a%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20ask%20Steve%20Eisman.%20The%20ultra-wealthy%20investor%20made%20a%20fortune%20by%20spotting%20the%20housing%20bubble%20before%20it%20burst.%20But%2C%20by%20his%20own%20admission%2C%20he'll%20likely%20never%20do%20so%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20financial%20crisis%20isn't%20happening%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20at%20Neuberger%20Berman%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Not%20this%20year.%20Not%20next%20year.%20Not%20in%202026.%20And%20probably%20not%20in%20the%20next%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20worry%20about%20the%20financial%20system%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Eisman%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20do%20%E2%80%94%20they%20seem%20to%20see%20it%20as%20a%20crisis%20a%20minute.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuccessfully%20shorting%20collateralized%20debt%20obligations%20in%20the%20mid-2000s%20changed%20Eisman's%20life%20forever%2C%20and%20Steve%20Carell%20immortalized%20his%20decisions%20in%20%26quot%3BThe%20Big%20Short%26quot%3B%20movie.%20But%20along%20with%20the%20fame%2C%20fortune%2C%20and%20respect%20have%20come%20a%20few%20annoyances%2C%20including%20a%20constant%20chorus%20of%20questions%20about%20where%20the%20next%20bubble%20is%2C%20or%20when%20the%20economy%20will%20implode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20I%20go%20on%20these%20shows%2C%20it's%20like%20they're%20begging%20me%20%E2%80%94%20begging%20me%20%E2%80%94%20to%20predict%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Eisman%20said%2C%20without%20being%20prompted%20by%20a%20question%20about%20bubbles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20portfolio%20manager%20has%20grown%20weary%20of%20being%20asked%20about%20bubbles%2C%20he%20said%20he's%20more%20amused%20by%20it%20than%20irritated.%20Negativity%20sells%2C%20but%20Eisman%20refuses%20to%20peddle%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20facts%20change%20and%20I%20saw%20something%2C%20I%20would%20say%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Eisman%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I'm%20not%20going%20out%20of%20my%20way%20to%20predict%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world%2C%20when%20I%20don't%20see%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20the%20next%20bubble%20isn't%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20follow%20markets%20without%20hearing%20from%20permabears.%20These%20pundits%20make%20eye-catching%2C%20fear-inducing%20predictions%20and%20cling%20to%20them%20for%20eternity%2C%20or%20until%20they%20come%20true.%20These%20warnings%20need%20not%20change%20and%20are%20only%20occasionally%20updated%20based%20on%20data%20that%20supports%20their%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20common%20narratives%20among%20permabears%20is%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdebt-crisis-us-economy-federal-reserve-mortgages-credit-bubble-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20national%20debt%20burden%20will%20become%20unbearable%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20causing%20a%20global%20economic%20disaster.%20In%20this%20scenario%2C%20plunging%20confidence%20in%20the%20US%20dollar%20costs%20the%20greenback%20its%20status%20as%20the%20world's%20reserve%20currency%2C%20while%20US%20Treasuries%20shed%20their%20value%20and%20become%20worth%20little%20more%20than%20the%20paper%20they're%20printed%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBearish%20commentators%20have%20sounded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-financial-crisis-national-debt-deficit-leon-cooperman-billionaire-omega-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethese%20warnings%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20about%20four%20decades%2C%20Eisman%20noted%2C%20and%20they're%20unlikely%20to%20stop%20anytime%20soon.%20The%20ultra-wealthy%20investor%20is%20convinced%20that%20such%20a%20doomsday%20scenario%20is%20unrealistic%2C%20as%20he%20can't%20begin%20to%20imagine%20what%20could%20cause%20the%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20an%20entire%20global%20financial%20system%20that%20works%2C%20functions%2C%20is%20embedded%20in%20the%20US%20dollar%20and%20US%20treasuries%2C%26quot%3B%20Eisman%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20a%20lot%20to%20break%20such%20a%20system.%20And%20having%20more%20federal%20debt%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20is%20going%20to%20do%20it.%20Something%20really%20calamitous%20has%20to%20happen%2C%20and%20I%20just%20don't%20see%20any%20of%20that%20happening.%20I%20just%20don't%20see%20it%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20dollar%20and%20economy%20are%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20global%20financial%20ecosystem.%20If%20they%20imploded%2C%20all%20the%20money%20in%20the%20world%20would%20need%20to%20go%20somewhere%20else%2C%20and%20it's%20unclear%20to%20Eisman%20where%20that%20would%20be.%20That%20makes%20the%20US%20akin%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fvideo%2Fbusiness%2Fthe-us-the-best-house-in-the-worst-neighborhood%2F2013%2F10%2F29%2F0f4d8eee-40d8-11e3-8b74-d89d714ca4dd_video.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20best%20house%20in%20a%20bad%20neighborhood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20borrow%20a%20decade-old%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'd%20have%20to%20have%20an%20alternative%20%E2%80%94%20some%20kind%20of%20government%20bond%20alternative%20to%20US%20Treasuries%2C%26quot%3B%20Eisman%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20China%3B%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20Europe%3B%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20Brazil.%20So%20until%20something%20else%20shows%20up%2C%20there's%20no%20alternative.%20I%20don't%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20worrying%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20no%2C%20crypto%20bros%3A%20Eisman%20said%20digital%20currencies%20aren't%20ready%20to%20be%20a%20big-scale%20solution%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20much%20as%20people%20like%20to%20invest%20in%20crypto%2C%20the%20size%20of%20crypto%20%E2%80%94%20even%20as%20big%20as%20it's%20gotten%20%E2%80%94%20is%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20Eisman%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20pimple%20compared%20to%20the%20size%20of%20the%20US%20global%20Treasury%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEisman%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20base%20a%20global%20financial%20system%20on%20a%20currency%20that%20goes%20up%20and%20down%20every%20day%20like%20a%20yo-yo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20is%20a%20meltdown%20off%20the%20table%2C%20but%20Eisman%20said%20the%20same%20is%20likely%20true%20of%20a%20run-of-the-mill%20recession%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20he%20acknowledges%20that%20growth%20is%20slowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEconomic%20downturns%20are%20usually%20caused%20by%20one%20of%20three%20factors%2C%20he%20said%3A%20a%20banking%20crisis%3B%20weak%20consumer%20spending%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffred.stlouisfed.org%2Fseries%2FDPCERE1Q156NBEA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emakes%20up%20two%20thirds%20of%20US%20GDP%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20and%20overinvestment%2C%20especially%20in%20industrial%20equipment%20or%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEisman%20made%20clear%20that%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%20financial%20crisis%20is%20off%20the%20table%20since%20banking%20regulations%20have%20been%20effective%2C%20allowing%20leverage%20to%20leave%20the%20system.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20money%20manager%20said%20consumers%20aren't%20loaded%20up%20on%20debt%2C%20which%20is%20an%20encouraging%20sign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20some%20may%20equate%20the%20tsunami-sized%20wave%20of%20investment%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20heavy%20investments%20in%20telecom%20infrastructure%20during%20the%20dot-com%20boom%2C%20Eisman%20believes%20it's%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-internet-dotcom-bubble-tech-stocks-nvidia-market-crash-gordon-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapples-to-oranges%20comparison%3C%2Fa%3E.%20AI%20may%20no%20longer%20be%20in%20its%20infancy%2C%20but%20