quot%3Bdaughter%26quot%3B%20and%20declaring%20he%20wanted%20a%20child%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20would%20reveal%20the%20man's%20identity%20to%20the%20special%20police%20team%20formed%20by%20the%20Kerala%20government%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20multiple%20cases%20of%20alleged%20sexual%20assault%20in%20Mollywood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%2018%20and%20in%20my%20first%20year%20of%20college...%20I%20came%20from%20a%20very%20sheltered%20background%20and%20my%20parents%20knew%20nothing%20about%20movies.%20This%20opportunity%20(to%20act%20in%20a%20Tamil%20film)%20came%20through%20my%20college%20theatre%20contact.%20As%20a%20child%20I%20was%20enamoured%20by%20the%20actor%20Revathy%2C%20who%20lived%20near%20my%20house%20at%20that%20time...I%20was%20in%20a%20fantasy%20world.%20So%20I%20went%20for%20a%20screen%20test%20with%20this%20couple...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20a%20child%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20Sowmya%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20indicated%20her%20family%20had%20been%20arm-twisted%20into%20allowing%20her%20to%20act%2C%20saying%20the%20director%20told%20her%20father%20they%20had%20spent%20large%20amounts%20of%20money%20on%20her%20screen%20test.%20This%20was%20after%20Sowmya's%20red%20flags%3B%20%26quot%3B...%20I%20said%20I%20wasn't%20comfortable%20with%20the%20man.%20I%20said%20this%20at%20my%20first%20meeting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Sowmya%20told%20NDTV%20she%20felt%20%26quot%3Bobligated%26quot%3B%20to%20act%20in%20that%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20first%20outdoor%20shoots%20he%20didn't%20speak%20to%20me.%20The%20agreement%20was%20that%20his%20wife%20would%20be%20the%20director%20but%20that%20was%20on%20paper...%20in%20reality%20he%20was%20directing%20the%20whole%20movie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20I%20was%20under%20his%20control...%20and%20he%20gave%20me%20the%20'angry%20silent%20treatment'%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20men%20are%20used%20to%20doing.%20And%20because%20of%20our%20conditioning%20in%20patriarchy...%20about%20authority%20figures%2C%20particularly%20intimidating%20men%20who%20express%20anger%20very%20easily%2C%20I%20was%20very%20scared%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESowmya%2C%20fighting%20to%20keep%20her%20emotions%20in%20check%2C%20then%20outlined%20how%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bgroomed%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20man%20who%20claimed%20her%20as%20his%20daughter%2C%20and%20whose%20own%20daughter%20had%20left%2C%20accusing%20him%20of%20rape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20but%20they%20told%20me%20she%20(the%20couple's%20daughter)%20was%20lying.%20So%20they%20brought%20me%20into%20their%20home...%20I%20was%20a%20teenager%20who%20was%20rebellious%20at%20home%20and%20suddenly%20this%20couple%20was%20nice%20to%20me%2C%20bribing%20me%20with%20good%20food%20and%20milkshakes%2C%20and%20telling%20me%20good%20things.%20That%20was%20the%20grooming%20process...%20he%20knew%20fully%20well%20what%20he%20was%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20firmly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20Sowmya%20told%20NDTV%2C%20the%20sexual%20assault%20and%20rape%20took%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20fine%20day%2C%20when%20his%20wife%20wasn't%20around%2C%20this%20man%2C%20while%20calling%20me%20his%20daughter%2C%20kissed%20me.%20I%20completely%20froze.%20I%20was%20so%20desperate%20to%20tell%20my%20friends%20but%20couldn't...%20I%20was%20ashamed%2C%20thinking%20I%20had%20done%20something%20wrong%20and%20that%20I%20was%20obligated%20to%20be%20nice%20to%20this%20man...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20continued%20going%20for%20practice%2C%20for%20dance%20rehearsals...%20every%20day%20I%20went%20back%20and%20gradually%2C%20step%20by%20step%2C%20this%20man%20completely%20used%20my%20body%20to%20his%20advantage.%20At%20some%20point%20he%20forced%20himself%20on%20me...%20so%20he%20raped%20me.%20This%20went%20on%20for%20close%20to%20a%20year%20while%20I%20was%20in%20college.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20time%20Sowmya%20said%20the%20man%20repeatedly%20called%20her%20his%20%26quot%3Bdaughter%26quot%3B%20and%20also%20that%20he%20wanted%20a%20child%20with%20her.%20%26quot%3BHe%20messed%20with%20my%20brain...%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20the%20anger%20palpable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sexual%20abuse%20continued%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%20as%20well%3B%20Sowmya%20did%20three%20films%20that%20were%20hits%20back%20in%20the%20'90s.%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BA%20co-star%20who%20sexually%20abused%20me%20has%20now%20been%20named%20in%20the%20Hema%20Committee%20report%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bdirectors%2C%20actors%2C%20and%20technicians%20abused%20me.%20There%20were%20also%20rights%20violations.%20One%20person%20spat%20pan%20on%20me.%26quot%3B%20When%20asked%20if%20there%20was%20consent%2C%20she%20said%20%26quot%3BNo%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20took%2030%20years%20for%20me%20to%20heal%20and%20recover%20from%20this%20sense%20of%20'shame'...%20I%20encourage%20survivors%20to%20report%20all%20such%20abuse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fm-mukesh-need-not-resign-as-mla-amid-metoo-allegations-cpi-m-6461561%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMukesh%20Need%20Not%20Resign%20As%20MLA%20Amid%20%23MeToo%20Claims%3A%20Kerala's%20CPIM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERape%20and%20assault%20allegations%20against%20senior%20Malayalam%20actors%20and%20film%20directors%20have%20been%20pouring%20in%20since%20the%20Justice%20Hema%20Committee%20report%20was%20released%20last%20month.%20Multiple%20cases%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20top%20actors%2C%20including%20Mukesh%2C%20who%20is%20also%20an%20MLA%20with%20the%20ruling%20CPIM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fi-have-2-daughters-we-need-tamil-f