..%20following%20a%20vicious%20attack%20by%20her%20boyfriend%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Uganda%20Olympic%20Committee%2C%20Donald%20Rukare%2C%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20cowardly%20and%20senseless%20act%20that%20has%20led%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20great%20athlete.%20Her%20legacy%20will%20continue%20to%20endure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20a%20man%20identified%20as%20Cheptegei's%20partner%2C%20Dickson%20Ndiema%20Marangach%2C%20doused%20her%20with%20petrol%20and%20set%20her%20alight%20on%20Sunday%20at%20her%20home%20in%20Endebess%20in%20the%20western%20county%20of%20Trans-Nzoia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20just%20weeks%20after%20Cheptegei%2C%2033%2C%20had%20taken%20part%20in%20the%20marathon%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20where%20she%20was%20placed%2044th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECheptegei%20suffered%20burns%20to%2080%20percent%20of%20her%20body%20in%20the%20attack%2C%20the%20acting%20head%20of%20the%20facility%20where%20she%20was%20being%20treated%20told%20reporters%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20her%20organs%20failed%20last%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20medic%20at%20the%20facility%2C%20the%20Moi%20Teaching%20and%20Referral%20Hospital%20(MTRH)%2C%20told%20AFP%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20nurse%20who%20had%20been%20treating%20Cheptegei%20said%20she%20died%20at%205%3A00%20am%20(0200%20GMT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20medical%20counsellor%20at%20the%20hospital%20had%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Cheptegei's%20condition%20had%20worsened%20and%20that%20she%20had%20developed%20a%20sepsis%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETributes%20poured%20in%20for%20the%20athlete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20deeply%20saddened%20to%20announce%20the%20passing%20of%20our%20athlete%2C%20Rebecca%20Cheptegei%2C%20early%20this%20morning%2C%20who%20tragically%20fell%20victim%20to%20domestic%20violence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Uganda%20Athletics%20Feder