arangach%20was%20also%20injured%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20sustaining%2030%20percent%20burns%20on%20his%20body.%20His%20current%20condition%20is%20not%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20said%20they%20were%20a%20couple%20who%20%26quot%3Bconstantly%20had%20family%20wrangles%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20on%20Cheptegei%20has%20again%20thrown%20a%20spotlight%20on%20domestic%20violence%20in%20Kenya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENjeri%20Wa%20Migwi%2C%20a%20feminist%20activist%20who%20founded%20Usikimye%2C%20an%20organisation%20that%20fights%20gender-based%20violence%2C%20said%20of%20her%20death%3A%20%26quot%3BYes%20this%20is%20Femicide.%20We%20must%20end%20Femicide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assault%20comes%20two%20years%20after%20Kenyan-born%20athlete%20Damaris%20Mutua%20was%20found%20dead%20in%20Iten%2C%20a%20world-famous%20running%20hub%20in%20the%20Rift%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%202021%2C%20record-breaking%20Kenyan%20runner%20Agnes%20Tirop%2C%2025%2C%20was%20found%20stabbed%20to%20death%20at%20her%20home%20in%20Iten%20in%202021.%20Her%20estranged%20husband%20is%20on%20trial%20over%20her%20murder%20and%20has%20denied%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELatest%20figures%20from%20the%20Kenya%20National%20Bureau%20of%20Statistics%20published%20in%20January%202023%20found%20that%2034%20percent%20of%20women%20in%20the%20country%20had%20experienced%20physical%20violence%20since%20the%20age%20of%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725524040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F2ci8a84o_cs_625x300_05_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fathletics%2Folympic-runner-rebecca-cheptegei-dies-after-partner-sets-her-on-fire-report-reveals-details-6495779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ugandan%20Olympian%20Rebecca%20Cheptegei%20died%20in%20