Cp%3EIndia%20is%20likely%20to%20soon%20overtake%20China%20as%20the%20most%20influential%20in%20a%20key%20emerging%20markets%20index%2C%20pulling%20in%20more%20foreign%20funds%20and%20adding%20fuel%20to%20a%20stock%20market%20rally%20that%2C%20though%20already%20among%20the%20best%20globally%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bonly%20past%20the%20halfway%20mark%26quot%3B%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20weightage%20in%20the%20MSCI%20emerging%20markets%20index%20rose%20to%2019.8%25%20after%20a%20rejig%20in%20August%2C%20closing%20in%20on%20China's%2024.2%25.%20India's%20weightage%20has%20steadily%20increased%20from%209.2%25%20in%20December%202020%2C%20while%20China's%20has%20dropped%20from%2039.1%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20rising%20weight%20essentially%20means%20more%20absolute%20foreign%20flows%2C%26quot%3B%20analysts%20led%20by%20Ridham%20Desai%20said%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20context%20of%20India%20being%20underweight%20in%20the%20average%20emerging%20markets%20portfolio%2C%20this%20is%20even%20better%20for%20foreign%20portfolio%20flows.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20portfolio%20investors%20(FPIs)%20have%20bought%20shares%20worth%20531.78%20billion%20rupees%20(%246.33%20billion)%20so%20far%20in%202024%2C%20and%20have%20remained%20net%20buyers%20since%20June%2C%20bolstered%20by%20policy%20continuity%20after%20the%20country's%20elections%20and%20an%20imminent%20start%20to%20global%20interest%20rate%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20sustained%20inflows%20from%20domestic%20institutional%20investors%2C%20mutual%20funds%20and%20retail%20traders%20have%20helped%20power%20the%20benchmark%20Nifty%2050%20to%20record%20highs.%20Its%2016%25%20jump%20this%20year%20is%20more%20than%20most%20other%20markets%2C%20including%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Desai%20expects%20the%20rally%20to%20continue%20as%20fiscal%20consolidation%20allows%20private%20borrowing%20and%20spending%20to%20fuel%20the%20next%20leg%20of%20earnings%20growth%20and%20as%20higher%20FII%20inflows%20will%20keep%20liquidity%20in%20surplus%2C%20lending%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20we%20are%20only%20past%20the%20halfway%20mark%20in%20the%20current%20bull%20market.%20A%20bull%20market%20peak%20for%20India%20is%20possibly%20still%20in%20the%20future%20and%20the%20weight%20in%20the%20EM%20index%20could%20have%20some%20more%20distance%20to%20travel%20before%20it%20peaks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorgan%20Stanley%20retained%20India%20as%20its%20top%20pick%20among%20emerging%20markets%20and%20second%20favourite%2C%20behind%20Japan%2C%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20stocks%2C%20it%20prefers%20cyclicals%20over%20defensives%20and%20large-caps%20over%20small-caps.%20And%20among%20sectors%2C%20it%20is%20'overweight'%20on%20financials%2C%20technology%2C%20consumer%20discretionary%20and%20industrials%2C%20and%20is%20'underweight'%20on%20others.%20(%241%20%3D%2083.9690%20Indian%20rupees)%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725522720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fdtdmdblg_bombay-stock-exchange-bse-generic-reuters_625x300_05_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-to-soon-top-china-among-emerging-global-markets-morgan-stanley-6495638%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20is%20likely%20to%20soon%20overtake%20China%20as%20the%20most%20influential%20in%20a%20key%20emerging%20markets%20index%2C%20pulling%20in%20more%20foreign%20funds%20and%20adding%20fuel%20to%20a%20stock%20market%20rally%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Bonly%20past%20the%20halfway%20mark%26quot%3B%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-to-soon-top-china-among-emerging-global-markets-morgan-stanley-6495638%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BInsurance%20Arrest%20By%20CBI%26quot%3B%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Argues%20For%20Bail%20In%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArguing%20for%20bail%20in%20the%20CBI%20case%20against%20him%20in%20connection%20with%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20today%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20central%20agency%20did%20an%20%26quot%3Binsurance%20arrest%26quot%3B%20after%20they%20realised%20that%20he%20could%20get%20bail%20in%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20has%20earlier%20granted%20interim%20bail%20to%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20in%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20case%20against%20him%2C%20but%20he%20remains%20in%20jail%20in%20the%20CBI%20case.%20This%20means%20that%20if%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20gives%20him%20the%20relief%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20will%20walk%20out%20of%20prison%20after%20over%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20arrested%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20on%20June%2026.%20The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20on%20August%205%20upheld%20his%20arrest%20as%20legal%20and%20said%20the%20CBI%20was%20able%20to%20establish%20that%20the%20AAP%20leader%20could%20influence%20witnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArguing%20for%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20before%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Surya%20Kant%20and%20Justice%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%20said%20this%20is%20an%20unprecedented%20matter.%20The%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20got%20relief%20twice%20under%20the%20stringent%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act.%20The%20CBI%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20done%20as%20%26quot%3Binsurance%20arrest%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20arrested%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20after%20two%20years.%20%26quot%3BThree%20court%20orders%20are%20in%20my%20favour.%20This%20is%20an%20insurance%20arrest%2C%20so%20that%20he%20can%20be%20kept%20in%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20needs%20to%20address%20three%20questions%20--%20is%20there%20a%20flight%20risk%3F%20will%20he%20tamper%20with%20evidence%3F%20will%20he%20influence%20witnesses%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20basis%20for%20CBI's%20arrest%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20was%20not%20cooperating.%20This%20issue%2C%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said%2C%20had%20been%20addressed%20in%20the%20past%20judgments%20that%20say%20an%20accused%20cannot%20be%20expected%20to%20incriminate%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20is%20a%20constitutional%20functionary%20and%20cannot%20be%20a%20flight%20risk.%20There%20can't%20be%20tampering%2C%20there%20are%20lakhs%20of%20documents%2C%20five%20chargesheets%20have%20been%20filed.%20There%20is%20also%20no%20risk%20of%20influencing%20witnesses.%20The%20triple%20test%20for%20bail%20is%20in%20my%20favour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20person%20was%20found%20fit%20for%20release%20twice%2C%20once%20by%20Supreme%20Court%20too%20even%20under%20higher%20threshold%20of%20Section%2045%20(of%20PMLA).%20I%20am%20the%20most%20captive%20interrogatee%20you%20can%20find%2C%20ever.%20Just%20for%20insurance%20you%20arrested!%20No%20substantial%20material%20was%20demonstrated%20before%20special%20judge%20to%20justify%20my%20arrest%2C%20grounds%20were%20vague%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20Justice%20Kant%20said%20while%20the%20bench%20will%20hear%20both%20sides%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20are%20wondering%20how%20long%20we%20should%20hear%20in%20a%20bail%20matter%2C%20do%20ordinary%20mortals%20get%20this%20much%20time%3F%26quot%3B%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20SV%20Raju%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20CBI%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20as%20much%20time%20as%20him%20(Singhvi)%2C%20at%20least.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singhvi%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20glad%20my%20lordships%20pointed%20that%20out.%20I%20will%20take%20till%2012%20so%20we%20can%20finish%20by%20lunch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI's%20counsel%20asked%20if%20Mr%20Singhvi%20is%20arguing%20on%20bail%20or%20arrest%20and%20that%20he%20cannot%20mix%20the%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTriple%20test%20satisfied%20fully.%20Every%20other%20possible%20co-accused%20has%20been%20released.%20I%20am%20taking%20about%20same%2C%20Vijay%20Nair%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%20and%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20said%20multiple%20chargesheets%20have%20been%20filed.%20%26quot%3BProlonged%20incarceration%20cannot%20be%20there%2C%20is%20the%20triple%20test%20satisfied%3F%20yes%20it%20is...%20all%20the%20judgments%20held%20on%20these%20points...%20in%20the%20Manish%20Sisodia%20judgment%2C%20the%20court%20held%20that%20in%20this%20particular%20case%20of%20excise%20policy%2C%20trial%20is%20impossible%20to%20finish.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bsnakes%20and%20ladders%26quot%3B%20expression%20used%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20while%20granting%20bail%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20party%20colleague%20Sisodia%20to%20refer%20to%20how%20the%20petitioner%20was%20being%20made%20to%20go%20to%20separate%20courts%20in%20a%20cycle.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20used%20a%20very%20felicitous%20phrase%2C%20snakes%20and%20ladders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposing%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20petition%2C%20the%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20said%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20had%20asked%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20to%20go%20to%20the%20lower%20court%20for%20bail%2C%20but%20he%20still%20filed%20the%20petition%20before%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20approached%20the%20High%20court%20without%20going%20to%20the%20sessions%20court.%20This%20is%20my%20preliminary%20objection.%20On%20merits%2C%20trial%20court%20could%20have%20seen%20it%20first.%20The%20high%20court%20was%20made%20to%20see%20merits%20and%20it%20can%20only%20be%20in%20exceptional%20cases.%20In%20ordinary%20cases%2C%20sessions%20court%20has%20to%20be%20approached%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20came%20here%20and%20then%20they%20approached%20high%20court%20and%20then%20again%20they%20came%20to%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20then%20this%20court%20decided%20the%20matter.%20This%20is%20the%20snake%20and%20ladder%20they%20were%20talking%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20never%20pointed%20out%20any%20exceptional%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20because%20the%20person%20is%20influential%2C%20it%20can%20keep%20playing%20snake%20and%20ladder%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725522720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fl90rukv_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_21_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-arvind-kejriwal-walk-free-key-hearing-in-supreme-court-today-6494494%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20hearing%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20petitions%20seeking%20bail%20and%20challenging%20his%20arrest%20in%20the%20CBI%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20capital's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-arvind-kejriwal-walk-free-key-hearing-in-supreme-court-today-6494494%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fans%20hail%20Hyun%20Bin%20in%20latest%20%E2%80%98Harbin%E2%80%99%20teaser%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725522491000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113087959%2Cimgsize-109602.cms%22%2C%