als%20to%20escape%20charges%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chargesheet%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kannada%20actor%20is%20among%2017%20people%2C%20including%20his%20friend%20actor%20Pavithra%20Gowda%2C%20who%20are%20in%20judicial%20custody%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20his%20fan%20Renukaswamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2033-year-old%20fan%20had%20allegedly%20sent%20obscene%20messages%20to%20Pavithra%20Gowda%2C%20after%20which%20he%20was%20allegedly%20beaten%20to%20death.%20His%20body%20was%20found%20near%20a%20stormwater%20drain%20in%20Bengaluru's%20Sumanahalli%20on%20June%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725522420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fvja25m_renukaswamy-_625x300_05_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-murder-case-against-actor-darshan-photos-of-assault-on-victim-surface-6495168%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Renukaswamy%20Murder%20Case%3A%20In%20a%20new%20twist%20in%20the%20kidnap%20and%20murder%20case%20against%20Kannada%20actor%20Darshan%2C%20photos%20allegedly%20showing%20the%20victim%20Renukaswamy%20being%20tortured%20before%20his%20death%20have%20surfaced%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-murder-case-against-actor-darshan-photos-of-assault-on-victim-surface-6495168%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Entirely%20baseless%2C%20fabricated'%3A%20China%20rejects%20New%20Zealand's%20spy%20report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725522298000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113087953%2Cimgsize-25580.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fentirely-baseless-fabricated-china-rejects-new-zealands-spy-report%2Farticleshow%2F113084468.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%