%22FBI%20Had%20Alerted%20Cops%20Of%20Teen%20Who%20Shot%20Dead%204%20At%20US%20School%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%2014-year-old%20student%20who%20killed%20four%20of%20his%20schoolmates%20in%20US's%20Georgia%20was%20questioned%20last%20year%20by%20police%20about%20online%20threats%2C%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(FBI)%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202023%2C%20Colt%20Gray%20was%20questioned%20by%20police%20who%20believed%20he%20was%20behind%20internet%20posts%20that%20contained%20images%20of%20guns%2C%20warning%20of%20a%20school%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20said%20its%20National%20Threat%20Operations%20Center%20had%20alerted%20local%20law%20enforcement%20after%20receiving%20tips%20about%20%26quot%3Bonline%20threats%20to%20commit%20a%20school%20shooting%20at%20an%20unidentified%20location%20and%20time%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20location%20of%20the%20threats%20were%20determined%2C%20the%20police%20interviewed%20the%20teen%20and%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20teen%20denied%20sending%20the%20threats%2C%20his%20father%20told%20police%20that%20he%20had%20hunting%20guns%20in%20the%20house%20but%20the%20then%2013-year-old%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20have%20unsupervised%20access%20to%20them%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20time%2C%20there%20was%20no%20probable%20cause%20for%20an%20arrest%20or%20to%20take%20any%20additional%20law%20enforcement%20action%20on%20the%20local%2C%20state%20or%20federal%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20FBI%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20boy%20used%20an%20assault%20rifle%20to%20open%20fire%20in%20Apalachee%20High%20School%2C%20killing%20two%20teachers%20and%20two%20student%2C%20investigators%20say.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%20other%20students%20and%20one%20teacher%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20attack.%20Gray%20was%20arrested%20from%20the%20school%20premises%20and%20will%20be%20tried%20as%20an%20adult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20sent%20out%20a%20message%20to%20parents%20saying%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bcurrently%20in%20a%20hard%20lockdown%20after%20reports%20of%20gunfire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurvivors%20recounted%20the%20moment%20when%20Gray%20began%20attacking%20the%20students.%20One%20student%20told%20BBC%20that%20she%20saw%20him%20leave%20a%20class%20after%20a%20maths%20lesson%20and%20when%20he%20returned%20he%20had%20a%20gun%20in%20his%20hand.%20One%20of%20her%20classmates%20saw%20the%20gun%20and%20refused%20to%20open%20the%20door%20for%20Gray%20even%20as%20he%20continued%20to%20pound%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGray%20then%20moved%20to%20the%20next%20classroom%20and%20opened%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20BBC%2C%20this%20was%20the%2023rd%20US%20school%20shooting%20of%202024.%20So%20far%2011%20people%20have%20died%20and%2038%20have%20been%20injured%20in%20such%20attacks%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725512160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fenra0qjg_georgia-shooting_625x300_05_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teen-who-shot-dead-4-was-questioned-by-cops-over-threats-in-2023-6494163%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2014-year-old%20student%20who%20killed%20four%20of%20his%20schoolmates%20in%20US's%20Georgia%20was%20questioned%20last%20year%20by%20police%20about%20online%20threats%2C%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(FBI)%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teen-who-shot-dead-4-was-questioned-by-cops-over-threats-in-2023-6494163%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20About%20%26quot%3BAlaska%20Triangle%26quot%3B%20Where%20Over%2020%2C000%20People%20Mysteriously%20Vanished%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Bermuda%20Triangle%20is%20a%20region%20in%20the%20Atlantic%20Ocean%20notorious%20for%20mysterious%20disappearance.%20However%2C%20did%20you%20know%20about%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3BAlaska%20Triangle%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20area%20that%20has%20more%20unsolved%20missing%20person%20cases%20than%20anywhere%20else%20in%20the%20world%3F%20Located%20roughly%20around%20three%20points%20of%20Anchorage%20and%20Juneau%20in%20the%20south%2C%20and%20Utqiagvik%2C%20a%20northern%20coastal%20city%2C%20the%20Alaska%20Triangle%20has%20remained%20a%20mystery%20after%20the%20disappearance%20of%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20people.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EIFL%20Science%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20area%20first%20came%20to%20the%20public's%20attention%20in%20October%201972%2C%20when%20a%20small%20plane%20carrying%20two%20US%20politicians%20suddenly%20disappeared%20en%20route%20from%20Anchorage%20to%20Juneau.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2C%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iflscience.com%2Fwhy-over-20000-people-have-vanished-in-the-alaska-triangle-69957%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20US%20House%20Majority%20Leader%20Thomas%20Hale%20Boggs%20Sr%20and%20Alaska%20Congressman%20Nick%20Begich%20disappeared%20when%20flying%20in%20a%20light%20aircraft%20from%20Anchorage%20to%20Juneau%20alongside%20Mr%20Begich's%20aide%2C%20Russell%20Brown%2C%20and%20the%20pilot%2C%20Don%20Jonz.%20A%20massive%20search%20effort%20was%20launched%20to%20find%20the%20four%20missing%20people%2C%20however%2C%20the%20bodies%20nor%20the%20plane%20were%20ever%20discovered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20sparked%20several%20conspiracy%20theories%20as%20to%20what%20could've%20happened%20-%20particularly%20since%20Mr%20Boggs%20was%20a%20Warren%20Commission%20member%20(the%20official%20body%20created%20to%20investigate%20John%20F.%20Kennedy's%20assassination)%20and%20apparently%20did%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20findings%20the%20group%20had%20made%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2C%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indy100.com%2Fscience-tech%2Falaska-triangle-people-disappeared%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndy100%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20prominent%20case%20was%20Gary%20Frank%20Sotherden%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20New%20Yorker%20who%20travelled%20to%20the%20Alaskan%20wilderness%20in%20the%20mid-1970s%20to%20go%20hunting%20but%20never%20returned%20home.%20Two%20decades%20later%20in%201997%2C%20a%20human%20skull%20was%20found%20along%20the%20Porcupine%20River%20in%20northeastern%20Alaska%20and%20DNA%20was%20later%20received%20in%202022.%20It%20was%20concluded%20the%20skull%20belonged%20to%20Mr%20Sotherden%20and%20believed%20he%20most%20probably%20died%20after%20being%20mauled%20by%20a%20bear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgreek-woman-44-intentionally-starts-2-wildfires-to-watch-firefighters-and-flirt-with-them-6494024%5C%22%3EGreek%20Woman%2C%2044%2C%20Intentionally%20Starts%202%20Wildfires%20To%20%26quot%3BWatch%20Firefighters%26quot%3B%20And%20%26quot%3BFlirt%20With%20Them%26quot%3B%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20have%20offered%20various%20explanations%20for%20the%20disappearances.%20While%20some%20have%20suggested%20that%20there%20is%20unusual%20magnetic%20activity%20in%20the%20Alaska%20Triangle%2C%20others%20believe%20a%20lot%20of%20extraterrestrial%20aliens%20have%20been%20visiting%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20simpler%20explanations%20have%20been%20that%20it%20is%20vast%20land%20which%20is%20full%20of%20wilderness%20and%20natural%20dangers%20which%20can%20be%20the%20reason%20why%20people%20have%20gone%20missing%20and%20never%20been%20found%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20perhaps%2C%20like%20the%20Bermuda%20Triangle%2C%20this%20mystery%20will%20never%20be%20solved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIFLScience%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%20that%20the%20area%20is%20full%20of%20%26quot%3Buntouched%20wilderness%26quot%3B%2C%20